{"tid":610480,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【Musk教徒】FCC批准SpaceX在美國及全球提供寬頻衛星服務","createTime":"2018-03-30T03:49:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-30T13:23:43.000Z","uid":141116,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1cfdcebca31418e5333e1163cca0b6495cb678d3","tid":610480,"uid":141116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T03:49:45.000Z","msg":"美國FCC周四表示，已經批准SpaceX在美國及全球提供衛星寬頻服務。<br />\n<br />\n　　FCC在聲明中說，這是他們第一次批准美國授權的衛星群用新一代近地軌道衛星技術提供寬頻服務。SpaceX想建一個衛星系統，由4425個衛星組成，美國當局允許它使用Ka(20/30 GHz)和Ku (11/14 GHz)頻段在全球提供互聯網連接服務。<br />\n<br />\n　　按照計劃，從2019年開始，SpaceX將會開始組建衛星群，它的綽號叫作「Starlink」。當部署的衛星至少達到800顆時，系統就會開始投入運營。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://apps.fcc.gov/edocs_public/attachmatch/DOC-349998A1.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.fcc.gov%2Fedocs_public%2Fattachmatch%2FDOC-349998A1.pdf&d=n9v%2FnEhgMshiD86tyvOXgNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=f17f5262\" target=\"_blank\">https://apps.fcc.gov/edocs_public/attachmatch/DOC-349998A1.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://iview.sina.com.tw/post/15657778\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fiview.sina.com.tw%2Fpost%2F15657778&d=n9v%2FnEhgMshiD86tyvOXgNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=669a150e\" target=\"_blank\">http://iview.sina.com.tw/post/15657778</a><br />\n<br />\nElon Musk 打救全世界仲用緊 56k 上網嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92903a69923966af3e9c15e1b8699d2f06e7348c","tid":610480,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T04:28:13.000Z","msg":"全球但唔包括支那"},{"pid":"dc9f410e72a7305cd2e9ae917c6bcfe1be56bf7d","tid":610480,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92903a69923966af3e9c15e1b8699d2f06e7348c","tid":610480,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T04:28:13.000Z","msg":"全球但唔包括支那"},"cit